<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Verify your identity</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: #f5f7fa; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
    <h1 style="color: #111827; margin: 0;">Verify your identity</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none;">
    <p>Please enter this code to verify your identity and complete your sign-in to Ostora.</p>

    <p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;">Verification code</p>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <div style="background: #f9fafb; display: inline-block; padding: 20px 40px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #d1d5db;">
        <span style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #111827;">{{otpCode}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="text-align: center; color: #4b5563; font-weight: 600;">(This code is valid for {{expiryMinutes}} minutes)</p>

    <p>For additional help, contact Ostora Support.</p>

    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; background: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px;">
      Ostora Platform will never email you and ask you to disclose or verify your password,
      credit card, or banking account number. If you receive a suspicious email with a link
      to update your account information, do not click the link. Instead, report the email
      to {{supportEmail}} for investigation.
    </p>

    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 30px 0;">

    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; text-align: center;">
      © 2026 Ostora. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
